OL,7,     Ga place of extreme weather,
OL,8,     Gwildlife, wilderness and ways of
OL,9,     Glife. She starts in Anchorage, on
OL,10,     Gthe edge of civilisation.
OL,11,G1300FSue Perkins: Lost in Alaska
